    "Future workIn terms of the limitations of this work, we acknowledge that the proposed method only supports input in the form of sequences of graph snapshots.",
    "The proposed method cannot handle other types of temporal graphs, such as sequences of graph actions accompanied by timestamps.",
    "Furthermore, real-world situations are highly dynamic and influenced by numerous factors.",
    "It is important to note that no one can accurately predict the future without any uncertainties or missing information.",
    "Our method is intended to provide results for reference purposes only."
